manifests.contents:
[workspace]
members = ["app", "domain", "infra"]
resolver = "2"

[workspace.dependencies]
anyhow = "1"
config = "0.15.15"
dotenvy = "0.15"
metrics = "0.24.2"
metrics-exporter-prometheus = "0.17.2"
serde_json = "1"
thiserror = "2.0.16"
tower = "0.5"
tracing = "0.1"
tracing-error = "0.2"

[workspace.dependencies.axum]
version = "0.8.4"
features = ["macros", "json"]

[workspace.dependencies.serde]
version = "1"
features = ["derive"]

[workspace.dependencies.sqlx]
version = "0.8.2"
features = ["runtime-tokio", "macros", "postgres", "uuid", "time", "migrate"]

[workspace.dependencies.time]
version = "0.3"
features = ["macros", "serde"]

[workspace.dependencies.tokio]
version = "1"
features = ["full"]

[workspace.dependencies.tower-http]
version = "0.6.6"
features = ["trace", "cors", "compression-full", "request-id", "util"]

[workspace.dependencies.tracing-subscriber]
version = "0.3"
features = ["env-filter", "fmt", "json"]

[workspace.dependencies.uuid]
version = "1"
features = ["v4", "serde"]

[workspace.package]
edition = "2021"
authors = ["Your Name <you@example.com>"]
license = "MIT"

[profile.release]
opt-level = "z"
lto = "fat"
codegen-units = 1
panic = "abort"
strip = true

[profile.release.package]

[package]
name = "app"
edition = "2024"
version = "0.0.1"

[dependencies.anyhow]
workspace = true

[dependencies.axum]
workspace = true

[dependencies.config]
workspace = true

[dependencies.domain]
path = "../domain"

[dependencies.dotenvy]
workspace = true

[dependencies.infra]
path = "../infra"

[dependencies.metrics]
workspace = true

[dependencies.metrics-exporter-prometheus]
workspace = true

[dependencies.serde]
workspace = true

[dependencies.sqlx]
workspace = true

[dependencies.thiserror]
workspace = true

[dependencies.time]
workspace = true

[dependencies.tokio]
workspace = true

[dependencies.tower]
workspace = true

[dependencies.tower-http]
workspace = true

[dependencies.tracing]
workspace = true

[dependencies.tracing-subscriber]
workspace = true

[dependencies.uuid]
workspace = true

[[bin]]
path = "src/main.rs"
name = "app"
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
edition = "2024"
required-features = []

[lib]
path = "src/lib.rs"
name = "app"
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
edition = "2024"
required-features = []
crate-type = ["lib"]

[package]
name = "domain"
edition = "2024"
version = "0.0.1"

[dependencies.anyhow]
workspace = true

[dependencies.serde]
workspace = true

[dependencies.thiserror]
workspace = true

[dependencies.uuid]
workspace = true

[lib]
path = "src/lib.rs"
name = "domain"
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
edition = "2024"
required-features = []
crate-type = ["lib"]

[package]
name = "infra"
edition = "2024"
version = "0.0.1"

[dependencies.anyhow]
workspace = true

[dependencies.domain]
path = "../domain"

[dependencies.sqlx]
workspace = true

[dependencies.uuid]
workspace = true

[lib]
path = "src/lib.rs"
name = "infra"
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
edition = "2024"
required-features = []
crate-type = ["lib"]
